Retriva Local Containerized Deployment
NOTICE

This deployment bundle orchestrates the following components:

1. Retriva Core components (Apache License 2.0):
   - retriva-core
   - retriva-gateway
   - retriva-webui

2. Third-party infrastructure (各自的许可证):
   - Qdrant (Apache License 2.0)
   - Apache Tika (Apache License 2.0)
   - Redis (BSD 3-Clause)
   - whisper.cpp (MIT License)

3. Retriva Pro extensions (proprietary, NOT covered by the Apache 2.0 license
   of the core):
   - retriva-mediawiki-connector (Retriva Pro Proprietary Commercial License
     Agreement — see LICENSE.retriva-pro in that repository)

Retriva Pro is the commercial bundle formed by Retriva Core plus proprietary
extension containers. Pro extensions are isolated behind the "pro" Docker
Compose profile and are only started when explicitly requested via
`./scripts/manage.sh up-pro` (or the `up-with-connectors` alias).

A default `./scripts/manage.sh up` deployment contains only Apache-2.0-licensed
code and does not pull, build, or run any Pro extension containers.

Each Pro extension repository contains its own license file describing the
terms under which it is distributed. Refer to those files for details.
